OL,4,CWales' level crossings need urgent
OL,5,Csafety changes, report says
OL,6, A driver was seriously hurt when their
OL,7, van was hit by a train at a level
OL,8, crossing where safety changes were
OL,9, first demanded 12 years before.
OL,11,FThey suffered life-changing injuries at
OL,12,Fthe private Smiths Lower Cefn crossing
OL,13,Fin Powys, last June.
OL,15,FA Rail Accident Investigation Branch
OL,16,F(RAIB) report found the driver may not
OL,17,Fhave known they needed to call the
OL,18,Fsignaller before crossing.
OL,20,FThe Department for Transport (DfT) said
OL,21,Fit agreed signs "needs updating".
